headline: Lennar (LEN) Valuation After Q4 2025 Margin Pressure And Earnings Decline
summary: Lennar (LEN) is back in focus after its fourth quarter fiscal 2025 update showed revenue and earnings per share down sharply year over year, as margin pressure weighed on gross and operating profits. See our latest analysis for Lennar. The quarterly results and recent updates, including the new Dry Canyon active adult community and the latest dividend declaration, come after a choppy year for investors, with a 1 year total shareholder return decline of 15.57% and a 5 year total shareholder...
